OL,3,CInquest fails to determine cause of
OL,4,Cfatal explosion because of lack of
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FAn inquest has failed to determine the
OL,8,Fcause of an explosion which killed a
OL,9,F68-year-old man because of a lack of
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,FBrian Davies was killed after
OL,13,Fsuffering chest and neck injuries in
OL,14,Fthe incident on March 13, 2023, when
OL,15,Fhis home on Clydach Road, Morriston,
OL,16,FSwansea, was destroyed in the blast,
OL,17,Fsending debris across the road and
OL,18,Fnearby streets.
