OL,7,FA week-long inquest into his death at
OL,8,FSwansea Guildhall found that Mr Davies
OL,9,Fdied in an explosion, but could not
OL,10,Fdetermine the cause of the explosion
OL,11,Fdue to a lack of evidence.
OL,13,FThe coroner apologised to Mr Davies'
OL,14,Ffamily after the inquest was unable to
OL,15,Fgive them a "definitive answer on the
OL,16,Factual cause of the explosion".
