OL,7,FHis family had previously raised
OL,8,Fconcerns during proceedings about the
OL,9,Finvestigation which followed the
OL,10,Fexplosion, saying they felt "let down"
OL,11,Fby the authorities over "major
OL,12,Fmistakes".
OL,14,FThe inquest heard how much of the
OL,15,Fevidence from the scene was
OL,16,F"compromised and incomplete".
