OL,7,FRicky Davies, Mr Davies' son,
OL,8,Fpreviously told the court: "As a
OL,9,Ffamily we feel major mistakes have
OL,10,Fbeen made and we have been massively
OL,11,Flet down by the authorities losing
OL,12,Fevidence.
OL,14,F"We hope that harsh lessons have been
OL,15,Flearned and others don't have to
OL,16,Fendure the heartache we have had to
OL,17,Fface."
