OL,7,FWales and West Utilities, which
OL,8,Fmaintains the gas network across Wales
OL,9,Fand the south-west of England, was
OL,10,Frepresented during the inquest, and
OL,11,Fthe Health and Safety Executive was
OL,12,Falso in attendance.
OL,14,FHarry Lambert, representing Wales and
OL,15,FWest, said the police had "absolute"
OL,16,Fresponsibility for the gathering of
OL,17,Fevidence at the scene of the explosion
OL,18,Fand claimed there was no suggestion of
OL,19,Fproblems with the network.
