OL,7,FHe previously said: "The evidence is
OL,8,Fcompromised and incomplete. There is
OL,9,Fno evidence at all that the mains were
OL,10,Fthe cause of the gas explosion."
OL,12,FThe inquest heard that Mr Davies, a
OL,13,Fgrandfather-of-three, who worked in
OL,14,Fthe construction industry, had rented
OL,15,Fthe one-bedroom end of terrace
OL,16,Fproperty for about four years before
OL,17,Fhis death.
